The paper deals with data completion techniques and kernel methods applied to biological data sets for classification tasks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and social and information networks (cs.SI). However, since the focus is on kernel matrix completion, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely sub-categories.
